Yuuuuup, even less impressed.
My friend and I decided to share an order of their nem nuong cuon ($4.95) and a com tam bi cha suon nuong ($11.95), which is a rice plate with shredded pork, egg, pork chop, shrimp, and deep fried shrimp cake.
